{
  "url": "https://reflex.dev/docs/advanced-onboarding/configuration/\n",
  "sections": [
    "<h1 class=\"rt-Heading rt-r-size-6 font-x-large lg:font-xx-large scroll-m-[5rem] mt-4\" id=\"configuration\">Configuration</h1><svg class=\"lucide lucide-link !text-violet-11 invisible transition-[visibility_0.075s_ease-out] group-hover:visible mt-4 css-svt5ra\" fill=\"none\" height=\"18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">Reflex apps can be configured using a configuration file, environment variables, and command line arguments.</p><a class=\"rt-Text rt-reset rt-Link rt-underline-none flex flex-row items-center gap-6 hover:!text-violet-11 text-slate-12 cursor-pointer mb-2 transition-colors group css-1macts\" data-accent-color=\"\" href=\"https://reflex.dev/docs/advanced-onboarding/configuration/#configuration-file\">",
    "<h2 class=\"rt-Heading rt-r-size-6 font-large lg:font-x-large scroll-m-[5rem] mt-8\" id=\"configuration-file\">Configuration File</h2><svg class=\"lucide lucide-link !text-violet-11 invisible transition-[visibility_0.075s_ease-out] group-hover:visible mt-8 css-svt5ra\" fill=\"none\" height=\"18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">Running <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">reflex init</code> will create an <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">rxconfig.py</code> file in your root directory.\nYou can pass keyword arguments to the <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">Config</code> class to configure your app.</p><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">For example:</p><pre><div class=\"rt-Box relative mb-4\"><div class=\"rt-Box code-block css-1islnds\"><div><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color:#282c34;color:#abb2bf\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#7F848E;font-style:italic\"># rxconfig.py</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C678DD\">import</span><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\"> reflex </span><span style=\"color:#C678DD\">as</span><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\"> rx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\">config </span><span style=\"color:#56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\"> rx.</span><span style=\"color:#61AFEF\">Config</span><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\">(</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E06C75;font-style:italic\">    app_name</span><span style=\"color:#56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color:#98C379\">\"my_app_name\"</span><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#7F848E;font-style:italic\">    # Connect to your own database.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E06C75;font-style:italic\">    db_url</span><span style=\"color:#56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color:#98C379\">\"postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/my_db\"</span><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#7F848E;font-style:italic\">    # Change the frontend port.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E06C75;font-style:italic\">    frontend_port</span><span style=\"color:#56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color:#D19A66\">3001</span><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#ABB2BF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><button class=\"css-kobh7h\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-copy css-cqk0y8\" fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><rect height=\"14\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\" width=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg></button></div></div></pre><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">See the <a class=\"rt-Text rt-reset rt-Link rt-underline-always css-1io25ou\" data-accent-color=\"\" href=\"/docs/api-reference/config/\">config reference</a> for all the parameters available.</p><a class=\"rt-Text rt-reset rt-Link rt-underline-none flex flex-row items-center gap-6 hover:!text-violet-11 text-slate-12 cursor-pointer mb-2 transition-colors group css-1macts\" data-accent-color=\"\" href=\"https://reflex.dev/docs/advanced-onboarding/configuration/#environment-variables\">",
    "<h2 class=\"rt-Heading rt-r-size-6 font-large lg:font-x-large scroll-m-[5rem] mt-8\" id=\"environment-variables\">Environment Variables</h2><svg class=\"lucide lucide-link !text-violet-11 invisible transition-[visibility_0.075s_ease-out] group-hover:visible mt-8 css-svt5ra\" fill=\"none\" height=\"18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">You can override the configuration file by setting environment variables.\nFor example, to override the <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">frontend_port</code> setting, you can set the <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">FRONTEND_PORT</code> environment variable.</p><pre><div class=\"rt-Box relative mb-4\"><div class=\"rt-Box code-block css-1islnds\"><div><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color:#282c34;color:#abb2bf\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E06C75\">FRONTEND_PORT</span><span style=\"color:#56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color:#98C379\">3001</span><span style=\"color:#61AFEF\"> reflex</span><span style=\"color:#98C379\"> run</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><button class=\"css-kobh7h\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-copy css-cqk0y8\" fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><rect height=\"14\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\" width=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg></button></div></div></pre><a class=\"rt-Text rt-reset rt-Link rt-underline-none flex flex-row items-center gap-6 hover:!text-violet-11 text-slate-12 cursor-pointer mb-2 transition-colors group css-1macts\" data-accent-color=\"\" href=\"https://reflex.dev/docs/advanced-onboarding/configuration/#command-line-arguments\">",
    "<h2 class=\"rt-Heading rt-r-size-6 font-large lg:font-x-large scroll-m-[5rem] mt-8\" id=\"command-line-arguments\">Command Line Arguments</h2><svg class=\"lucide lucide-link !text-violet-11 invisible transition-[visibility_0.075s_ease-out] group-hover:visible mt-8 css-svt5ra\" fill=\"none\" height=\"18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">Finally, you can override the configuration file and environment variables by passing command line arguments to <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">reflex run</code>.</p><pre><div class=\"rt-Box relative mb-4\"><div class=\"rt-Box code-block css-1islnds\"><div><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color:#282c34;color:#abb2bf\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#61AFEF\">reflex</span><span style=\"color:#98C379\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#D19A66\"> --frontend-port</span><span style=\"color:#D19A66\"> 3001</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><button class=\"css-kobh7h\"><svg class=\"lucide lucide-copy css-cqk0y8\" fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><rect height=\"14\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\" width=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg></button></div></div></pre><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">See the <a class=\"rt-Text rt-reset rt-Link rt-underline-always css-1io25ou\" data-accent-color=\"\" href=\"/docs/api-reference/cli/\">CLI reference</a> for all the arguments available.</p><a class=\"rt-Text rt-reset rt-Link rt-underline-none flex flex-row items-center gap-6 hover:!text-violet-11 text-slate-12 cursor-pointer mb-2 transition-colors group css-1macts\" data-accent-color=\"\" href=\"https://reflex.dev/docs/advanced-onboarding/configuration/#customizable-app-data-directory\">",
    "<h2 class=\"rt-Heading rt-r-size-6 font-large lg:font-x-large scroll-m-[5rem] mt-8\" id=\"customizable-app-data-directory\">Customizable App Data Directory</h2><svg class=\"lucide lucide-link !text-violet-11 invisible transition-[visibility_0.075s_ease-out] group-hover:visible mt-8 css-svt5ra\" fill=\"none\" height=\"18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">The <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">REFLEX_DIR</code> environment variable can be set, which allows users to set the location where Reflex writes helper tools like Bun and NodeJS.</p><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">By default we use Platform specific directories:</p><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">On windows, <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">C:/Users/&lt;username&gt;/AppData/Local/reflex</code> is used.</p><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">On macOS, <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">~/Library/Application Support/reflex</code> is used.</p><p class=\"rt-Text font-normal text-slate-12 mb-4 leading-7\">On linux, <code class=\"rt-reset rt-Code rt-variant-soft code-style\" data-accent-color=\"\">~/.local/share/reflex</code> is used.</p></article>"
  ]
}